divs: sighting detailssighting report: it was at approximately 9:30 pm est on 3-19-05. i was outside with my friends during a clear night. we stopped playing when we spotted a large, elliptical flying object above us at about a 70 degree angle. it was either flying lower than a plane or much larger because we could see it clearly. there were lights on the top\bottom (2) and on the sides (2). the top\bottom lights flashed different colors that scattered around while the side lights stayed white. it maintained a relatively constant speed for 25 seconds until it sped up and away, emitting a strange, high-pitched "loooo" sound.
